title: Breakfast Bacon Stacks | Dan Churchill
description:
Australian health coach and cook Dan Churchill is taking the world by storm with his delicious and nutritious recipes.  These Breakfast Bacon Stacks of lean meat on grated sweet potato rostis with pan fried spinach and a lemon tahini mayonnaise are so good why restrict them to breakfast!

Check out more videos from Dan here https://www.youtube.com/user/danchurchillcooks or follow him online here http://danielchurchill.com.au/
